column5: You got my support Joey! I'll work on rallying some more for you here at work!
Bump!
Bump.
You have my vote Joey...
Just added another vote for you Joey
Thanks  I've slipped out of top 20 tho     You have to be in top 20 to qualify.  We'll get there this week hopefully.  Thanks again,  Joey
you are back to 20th
Come on guys! Joey needs a lot more votes than this to stay in the top 20!  We should be able to keep her at the top easily!  It is the power of OFC!
ttt
Come on folks, Joey deserves better than a 24th place showing.

So there's a new contest hosted by WFN called:  "WFN's A Great Day for Fishing with Joe Mercurio Contest"  I wonder if I could borrow a few votes from y'all.  I'd love to go fishing with Joe down in Florida, sounds like it would be awesome.  They asked for one of your fav days of fishing, so I posted the day I caught that huge carp on Lake Simcoe on New Years Day when Paul and I ice fished with Terry, that was a blast!!  Here is the link if anyone could send a vote my way.  I'd really appreciate it.  Thanks in advance  Vote Here  Joey
Is this how they did the election voting in Iraq?
voted
Only 'cuz yer perty!  Good luck!
No. Remember, this is how the elections are done in Florida.
You've got mine
I see that we can vote from the states on this one - done. 26th now - we can do much better than that.
Done.... voted.  Still 26th Good luck to ya Joey!!!
Managed to get you to 23rd, ways to go yet.....
You've got mine for the next 6 days.
voted.
I got you into the "the bubble"... 25th. Get a picture up there!
done
I tried, it didn't work.  I emailed them today to ask how and they said its too late to add a pic.  I was gonna put the one with the big carp, but oh well, too late.
hey I remember that day maybe we can do it again this winter...LOL  and  I voted
Here's a few more bumps for you.... got you down to 21 Cheers
you got my vote.
Done!

BOy they really keep track of you.  Looks like you can only vote once within a 24 hour period.  Kept trying this morning.  Funny ... it came back and finally said you can't vote for another 1 minute.   Anyway, today's vote is in there.   16th now.
Wow, thanks everyone, I was pleasantly surprised to see I'm in 15th place this morning.  You're all awesome!!  Joey
There's another bump towards #1 Joey
With the help of a few "friends" got your vote count up to 100 but still 16th.
Voted for ya.... Good Luck !!
I remember that report! good thing Carp don't have teeth! still an amazing angling feat hehe  Vote placed. Tony
Everybody hop on the bandwagon.  You've slipped to 17
